                    "script": "\t\"\"\"\n\t\tWritten By: Amitkumar Ravat\n\t\tWritten Date: 01/06/2024\n\t\tPurpose: close exceed popup and save cycle time in db. \n\t\"\"\"\n\ttry:\n\t\tpayload \u003d {\u0027Id\u0027:self.parent.getChild(\"cntExceedType\").getChild(\"drpExceedType\").props.value, \u0027operator_Id\u0027:self.view.params.operator_Id}\n\t\tsystem.perspective.sendMessage(\"saveExceedTime\", payload \u003d payload, scope\u003d\u0027page\u0027)\n\t\tsystem.perspective.closePopup(\u0027#exceed\u0027)\n\t\tself.parent.getChild(\"cntExceedType\").getChild(\"drpExceedType\").props.value \u003d -1\n\texcept:\t\n\t\tscreenName \u003d\u0027QualityPopup\u0027\n\t\tfilePath\u003dstr(\u0027Project_VECV/Operator Dashboard/QualityPopUp\u0027)  \n\t\terrorFunction \u003d str(\u0027Event:onActionPerformed-\u003e TabContainer/cntColumnTakeOut/btnSave\u0026Close\u0027)  \n\t\terrorType\u003dstr(\u0027Application\u0027)  \n\t\terrorCode \u003d str(Project_VECV.Common.GenerateUUID.getUniqueUUID())   \n\t\tdescription\u003dstr(sys.exc_info()[1]) #error description \n\t\tlineNumber\u003dstr(sys.exc_info()[2].tb_lineno) #lineno on which error \n\t\tProject_VECV.Configuration.Common.AddLogDetails.AddErrorLogs(screenName,filePath,errorFunction,errorType,errorCode,description,lineNumber)"
                  },
